2
00:01:19,920 --> 00:01:20,719
Ssss

3
00:01:22,439 --> 00:01:23,239
Ugh

4
00:01:26,519 --> 00:01:27,319
Ah

5
00:01:29,040 --> 00:01:29,840
Ssss

6
00:01:30,959 --> 00:01:31,760
Huahua

7
00:01:33,599 --> 00:01:34,120
Ssss

8
00:01:34,319 --> 00:01:34,920
Hey

9
00:01:36,560 --> 00:01:37,120
Hey

10
00:01:37,120 --> 00:01:37,920
This...

11
00:01:39,000 --> 00:01:39,560
I...

12
00:01:42,359 --> 00:01:43,159
Prince

13
00:01:50,159 --> 00:01:50,959
Serve the food

14
00:01:54,120 --> 00:01:56,760
I thank the Deer Prince for his gracious hospitality

15
00:01:56,799 --> 00:01:57,159
Ah

16
00:01:57,319 --> 00:01:59,799
The envoy has brought tremendous good news

17
00:02:00,359 --> 00:02:02,239
A mere banquet is hardly worth mentioning

18
00:02:03,599 --> 00:02:05,159
Once I become emperor

19
00:02:05,359 --> 00:02:06,599
I will surely reward you further

20
00:02:08,560 --> 00:02:09,960
You're too kind, Deer Prince

21
00:02:10,400 --> 00:02:12,000
On my way through Lucheng this time

22
00:02:12,120 --> 00:02:14,319
I found Lucheng's land flat and broad

23
00:02:14,439 --> 00:02:15,520
With houses neatly arranged

24
00:02:15,719 --> 00:02:18,960
Fertile fields, fine ponds, mulberry and bamboo

25
00:02:19,840 --> 00:02:20,840
Pathways crisscrossing

26
00:02:20,919 --> 00:02:21,960
Chickens and dogs heard all around

27
00:02:22,120 --> 00:02:24,520
Old and young alike living in joy

28
00:02:25,120 --> 00:02:28,520
The Deer Prince surely has the talent to govern

29
00:02:28,520 --> 00:02:30,879
And is the perfect choice for emperor

30
00:02:36,199 --> 00:02:37,000
Prince

31
00:02:38,360 --> 00:02:39,159
Hmm

32
00:02:41,719 --> 00:02:42,520
Hey

33
00:02:44,120 --> 00:02:46,560
The Prince Wants...

34
00:02:51,120 --> 00:02:51,759
Uh

35
00:02:51,759 --> 00:02:52,240
You

36
00:02:52,360 --> 00:02:52,879
Uh

37
00:02:52,879 --> 00:02:53,759
Don't get the wrong idea

38
00:03:02,520 --> 00:03:03,759
How dare you, Qi Zhi!

39
00:03:04,960 --> 00:03:06,840
You dared to tattoo my face?

40
00:03:08,360 --> 00:03:08,879
Prince, Prince!

41
00:03:09,520 --> 00:03:11,280
I just woke up too! I don't know anything!

42
00:03:12,039 --> 00:03:12,840
You don't know?

43
00:03:12,840 --> 00:03:13,639
Hmm

44
00:03:17,240 --> 00:03:18,159
Look at them

45
00:03:19,840 --> 00:03:20,960
Now look at me

46
00:03:21,719 --> 00:03:23,240
Now look at yourself

47
00:03:23,919 --> 00:03:25,520
Clearly you're the odd one out

48
00:03:27,199 --> 00:03:28,000
Hey

49
00:03:30,360 --> 00:03:31,159
Hey

50
00:03:32,520 --> 00:03:33,520
Where's my deer?

51
00:03:34,360 --> 00:03:35,319
Where's my deer?

52
00:03:35,599 --> 00:03:37,240
Hahaha

53
00:03:37,560 --> 00:03:38,159
Envoy Qi Zhi

54
00:03:38,719 --> 00:03:41,319
Turns out you're quite the flatterer

55
00:03:42,919 --> 00:03:45,159
He even found you the perfect husband

56
00:03:45,439 --> 00:03:46,520
Give Huahua back to me

57
00:03:46,560 --> 00:03:47,360
No way

58
00:03:48,439 --> 00:03:50,560
He hasn't agreed to marry me yet

59
00:03:50,759 --> 00:03:52,719
Do I have to handle that too?

60
00:03:53,039 --> 00:03:54,280
Of course you do

61
00:03:54,360 --> 00:03:56,319
Actually, Lucheng's prosperity

62
00:03:56,919 --> 00:03:58,719
Isn't entirely my doing

63
00:03:59,000 --> 00:04:00,560
Our nation's wealth and abundance

64
00:04:00,919 --> 00:04:02,240
Most of the credit

65
00:04:03,159 --> 00:04:04,520
Goes to him

66
00:04:05,159 --> 00:04:05,520
Look

67
00:04:06,319 --> 00:04:08,800
This is the divine deer Father bestowed on me

68
00:04:09,199 --> 00:04:11,439
It's said to be the last one in all Daliang

69
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:12,400
This deer

70
00:04:13,000 --> 00:04:14,360
Can attract wealth and treasures

71
00:04:14,560 --> 00:04:15,560
And ward off misfortune

72
00:04:16,279 --> 00:04:17,319
With it

73
00:04:18,160 --> 00:04:19,639
It's worth more than a million treasures

74
00:04:20,560 --> 00:04:21,240
So I call it

75
00:04:21,600 --> 00:04:23,600
The Deer of Myriad Treasures

76
00:04:23,920 --> 00:04:24,720
Hey

77
00:04:25,120 --> 00:04:26,720
You must be after my Deer of Myriad Treasures

78
00:04:27,800 --> 00:04:29,399
You wanted to drug us all

79
00:04:29,439 --> 00:04:30,600
And take the chance to steal my Deer of Myriad Treasures

80
00:04:30,720 --> 00:04:31,199
No, no, no

81
00:04:31,240 --> 00:04:31,600
Prince

82
00:04:31,600 --> 00:04:32,319
That makes no sense at all

83
00:04:32,399 --> 00:04:34,480
If I'd stolen your deer, why would I come back?

84
00:04:35,040 --> 00:04:36,240
I remember now

85
00:04:38,600 --> 00:04:40,079
I remember where we went last night

86
00:04:40,240 --> 00:04:41,040
Where?

87
00:04:46,839 --> 00:04:48,160
Aaaah!

88
00:04:51,160 --> 00:04:52,399
This humble one greets the Prince.

89
00:04:52,439 --> 00:04:52,720
Prince.

90
00:04:52,720 --> 00:04:53,560
Cut the nonsense.

91
00:04:54,319 --> 00:04:54,800
Hey.

92
00:04:55,800 --> 00:04:56,720
This writing on my face,

93
00:04:56,720 --> 00:04:57,800
did you tattoo it?

94
00:04:57,920 --> 00:04:58,720
Uh...

95
00:04:58,920 --> 00:04:59,560
Yes.

96
00:04:59,560 --> 00:05:00,199
How dare you!

97
00:05:02,160 --> 00:05:03,160
Who told you to do it?

98
00:05:03,800 --> 00:05:04,720
Was it him?

99
00:05:04,720 --> 00:05:05,360
Hmm?

100
00:05:05,360 --> 00:05:06,160
Uh...

101
00:05:07,519 --> 00:05:08,800
You insisted on it yourself, Prince.

102
00:05:09,079 --> 00:05:11,360
I couldn't even stop you!

103
00:05:11,759 --> 00:05:12,639
That's impossible.

104
00:05:13,360 --> 00:05:13,600
Behead him.

105
00:05:13,759 --> 00:05:13,959
Behead him!

106
00:05:14,759 --> 00:05:16,160
Spare me, Prince!

107
00:05:16,519 --> 00:05:17,399
I-I-I...

108
00:05:17,519 --> 00:05:18,759
Every word I said is true!

109
00:05:18,800 --> 00:05:19,560
Hey, wait.

110
00:05:20,639 --> 00:05:22,439
I think I'm remembering something.

111
00:05:22,759 --> 00:05:25,399
Tomorrow is your big day.

112
00:05:25,759 --> 00:05:28,639
I'll make you Prime Minister.

113
00:05:29,560 --> 00:05:31,120
What's the fun in being Prime Minister?

114
00:05:31,560 --> 00:05:34,160
Just deliver on your promise to Ouyang Yan.

115
00:05:35,639 --> 00:05:37,759
My happiness with my chicken friend depends on you.

116
00:05:37,759 --> 00:05:38,600
You don't trust me?

117
00:05:39,160 --> 00:05:40,639
I'm afraid you'll back out tomorrow morning.

118
00:05:40,639 --> 00:05:42,319
I'm a Prince of Daliang.

119
00:05:42,639 --> 00:05:43,839
My word is gold.

120
00:05:45,120 --> 00:05:45,480
Then how about this.

121
00:05:46,720 --> 00:05:48,800
I'll tattoo it on my body.

122
00:05:48,920 --> 00:05:49,839
No, no, no!

123
00:05:49,839 --> 00:05:50,279
Careful!

124
00:05:50,519 --> 00:05:50,839
No.

125
00:05:52,040 --> 00:05:52,439
Tattoo it...

126
00:05:53,120 --> 00:05:53,319
on my face.

127
00:05:54,360 --> 00:05:54,759
Hmph.

128
00:05:55,279 --> 00:05:55,639
Hmph.

129
00:05:55,920 --> 00:05:56,120
Hey.

130
00:05:56,160 --> 00:05:56,920
Hmph.

131
00:05:56,920 --> 00:05:57,720
Isn't this a tattoo shop?

132
00:05:58,720 --> 00:05:59,560
Let's walk in,

133
00:06:00,240 --> 00:06:01,040
and get a tattoo.

134
00:06:01,199 --> 00:06:02,000
Sounds good.

135
00:06:03,680 --> 00:06:03,920
Hey, hey, hey!

136
00:06:04,319 --> 00:06:05,079
Seen enough yet?

137
00:06:05,160 --> 00:06:06,160
Are you going to speak or not?

138
00:06:06,560 --> 00:06:08,360
You want me to drop my pants too?

139
00:06:09,319 --> 00:06:09,959
No need, no need!

140
00:06:11,560 --> 00:06:13,160
But this "The Prince Wants"

141
00:06:13,160 --> 00:06:14,279
what does it actually mean?

142
00:06:14,319 --> 00:06:15,199
What is it that you want?

143
00:06:15,360 --> 00:06:16,399
Go ask the Princess about that.

144
00:06:16,399 --> 00:06:17,600
What did I promise her, anyway?

145
00:06:18,120 --> 00:06:18,600
Oh, right.

146
00:06:18,600 --> 00:06:18,920
Hey.

147
00:06:19,439 --> 00:06:19,920
Boss.

148
00:06:20,639 --> 00:06:20,959
Let me ask you,

149
00:06:21,160 --> 00:06:23,519
when we came yesterday, was a girl following us?

150
00:06:24,920 --> 00:06:25,720
Uh...

151
00:06:26,360 --> 00:06:27,160
No, sir.

152
00:06:28,240 --> 00:06:29,879
Just the two of you.

153
00:06:34,920 --> 00:06:36,519
When I catch whoever made me get tattooed,

154
00:06:36,519 --> 00:06:37,639
I'll definitely behead him.

155
00:06:38,759 --> 00:06:39,160
Prince.

156
00:06:39,759 --> 00:06:40,759
Didn't I already tell you?

157
00:06:41,360 --> 00:06:43,160
You insisted on it yourself yesterday.

158
00:06:43,160 --> 00:06:43,959
Shut up.

159
00:06:44,920 --> 00:06:45,920
Or I'll behead you first.

160
00:06:48,399 --> 00:06:48,959
Now talk.

161
00:06:49,639 --> 00:06:50,839
Where do we go next?

162
00:06:50,839 --> 00:06:51,800
How would I know?

163
00:06:51,800 --> 00:06:52,920
I still want to find Ouyang Yan.

164
00:06:53,560 --> 00:06:54,920
Huahua must be in her hands.

165
00:06:56,040 --> 00:06:56,560
Prince.

166
00:06:56,800 --> 00:06:58,800
You left this purse here yesterday.

167
00:07:02,439 --> 00:07:03,519
Office supplies.

168
00:07:04,800 --> 00:07:05,360
Hsss.

169
00:07:05,560 --> 00:07:06,759
Hongru Academy.

170
00:07:12,240 --> 00:07:12,560
Hey

171
00:07:12,680 --> 00:07:14,079
Hello, brother-in-law!

172
00:07:14,079 --> 00:07:15,000
Brother-in-law!

173
00:07:16,160 --> 00:07:16,480
Brother-in-law, you're here!

174
00:07:16,560 --> 00:07:17,079
Huh?

175
00:07:17,399 --> 00:07:17,959
Who's this?

176
00:07:18,600 --> 00:07:19,160
Who?

177
00:07:19,399 --> 00:07:20,639
Brother-in-law, you're here for Xiaotong, right?

178
00:07:20,800 --> 00:07:21,560
Who?

179
00:07:21,759 --> 00:07:22,399
Who?

180
00:07:22,480 --> 00:07:22,759
Brother-in-law!

181
00:07:23,959 --> 00:07:24,319
Who?

182
00:07:24,959 --> 00:07:25,279
This...

183
00:07:25,519 --> 00:07:26,319
You've got the wrong person.

184
00:07:27,759 --> 00:07:28,560
Who are you all?

185
00:07:28,600 --> 00:07:28,920
Brother-in-law!

186
00:07:29,959 --> 00:07:30,480
Who?

187
00:07:30,920 --> 00:07:32,040
Did you miss us?

188
00:07:33,639 --> 00:07:34,600
They're calling you brother-in-law.

189
00:07:36,120 --> 00:07:36,560
Could it be...

190
00:07:36,759 --> 00:07:38,360
Did I do something weird yesterday?

191
00:07:38,519 --> 00:07:38,879
Huh?

192
00:07:40,720 --> 00:07:41,079
Husband!

193
00:07:41,160 --> 00:07:41,720
Huh?

194
00:07:42,079 --> 00:07:43,160
Miss, we're here on official business.

195
00:07:43,199 --> 00:07:43,639
Please behave yourself.

196
00:07:44,319 --> 00:07:44,920
Husband!

197
00:07:45,319 --> 00:07:46,240
What's wrong with you?

198
00:07:46,319 --> 00:07:47,279
I'm Xiaotong.

199
00:07:48,160 --> 00:07:48,439
This...

200
00:07:49,319 --> 00:07:50,120
Xiaotong?

201
00:07:50,600 --> 00:07:50,879
No, wait,

202
00:07:50,920 --> 00:07:51,639
Miss,

203
00:07:51,639 --> 00:07:53,240
calling me husband and brother-in-law,

204
00:07:53,240 --> 00:07:54,759
is this some kind of family inn?

205
00:07:55,360 --> 00:07:55,879
Husband!

206
00:07:56,439 --> 00:07:58,199
One night and you don't recognize me?

207
00:07:59,240 --> 00:07:59,600
Huh?

208
00:08:00,920 --> 00:08:02,160
Ladies, let me tell you,

209
00:08:02,439 --> 00:08:03,759
I had too much to drink last night.

210
00:08:03,800 --> 00:08:04,160
So,

211
00:08:04,160 --> 00:08:05,319
whatever I said,

212
00:08:05,319 --> 00:08:05,759
whatever I did,

213
00:08:05,759 --> 00:08:06,560
please don't take it seriously.

214
00:08:06,639 --> 00:08:08,160
How can you be like this?

215
00:08:10,040 --> 00:08:11,560
We got married last night!

216
00:08:11,839 --> 00:08:12,720
We drank the wedding wine,

217
00:08:13,160 --> 00:08:14,439
and even received the betrothal gifts!

218
00:08:14,439 --> 00:08:14,920
Really?

219
00:08:15,560 --> 00:08:16,759
That's right, that's right!

220
00:08:16,800 --> 00:08:17,319
Wait,

221
00:08:19,240 --> 00:08:20,360
we didn't consummate it, did we?

222
00:08:22,439 --> 00:08:23,160
No.

223
00:08:23,839 --> 00:08:24,319
It's all his fault.

224
00:08:25,199 --> 00:08:26,000
If it weren't for him,

225
00:08:26,639 --> 00:08:26,920
we...

226
00:08:27,480 --> 00:08:29,160
we'd have sealed the deal long ago.

227
00:08:29,399 --> 00:08:30,120
Thank goodness, thank goodness.

228
00:08:30,120 --> 00:08:31,199
Right.

229
00:08:31,360 --> 00:08:32,159
What did you say?

230
00:08:32,559 --> 00:08:32,919
Huh?

231
00:08:34,200 --> 00:08:35,919
You irresponsible, terrible man!

232
00:08:36,279 --> 00:08:36,840
I...

233
00:08:37,320 --> 00:08:38,360
Take your ring back!

234
00:08:38,919 --> 00:08:40,080
How can you do this?

235
00:08:42,600 --> 00:08:43,480
This is your ring, isn't it?

236
00:08:44,679 --> 00:08:45,840
I've never seen this ring before.

237
00:08:45,840 --> 00:08:46,000
Then...

238
00:08:46,320 --> 00:08:46,960
Yours?

239
00:08:47,399 --> 00:08:48,080
Oh my!

240
00:08:48,320 --> 00:08:49,919
Prince, you're here again.

241
00:08:50,399 --> 00:08:50,759
Oh my!

242
00:08:50,919 --> 00:08:51,120
Huh?

243
00:08:52,039 --> 00:08:52,320
Prince,

244
00:08:52,879 --> 00:08:54,360
what happened to your face?

245
00:08:57,159 --> 00:08:58,679
For two days in a row,

246
00:08:59,159 --> 00:09:00,559
you've graced our humble establishment.

247
00:09:01,320 --> 00:09:04,240
You truly honor our Hongru Academy.

248
00:09:05,559 --> 00:09:06,320
Indeed.

249
00:09:06,320 --> 00:09:07,039
Prince,

250
00:09:07,039 --> 00:09:08,879
are you quite pleased

251
00:09:09,159 --> 00:09:10,000
with our girls here?

252
00:09:10,000 --> 00:09:10,360
Shut up.

253
00:09:12,960 --> 00:09:14,240
A brothel

254
00:09:14,720 --> 00:09:15,919
calling itself an academy.

255
00:09:16,759 --> 00:09:18,240
That's downright shameless.

256
00:09:18,240 --> 00:09:19,039
Hmm.

257
00:09:19,919 --> 00:09:20,759
Prince,

258
00:09:21,399 --> 00:09:23,600
yesterday you were singing its praises.

259
00:09:23,919 --> 00:09:24,720
You even said

260
00:09:25,000 --> 00:09:27,600
expensing it would be a breeze.

261
00:09:27,639 --> 00:09:29,200
Right, exactly, that's what he said.

262
00:09:29,200 --> 00:09:30,320
Besides,

263
00:09:30,600 --> 00:09:31,799
as the ancient saying goes,

264
00:09:32,320 --> 00:09:34,120
"In books, one finds beauty like jade."

265
00:09:34,799 --> 00:09:35,919
Here at our place,

266
00:09:36,039 --> 00:09:38,840
each book is a girl.

267
00:09:39,159 --> 00:09:40,399
Isn't that right?

268
00:09:40,840 --> 00:09:41,679
Oh my, my.

269
00:09:41,759 --> 00:09:41,960
Enough.

270
00:09:41,960 --> 00:09:43,399
Don't play word games with me.

271
00:09:44,600 --> 00:09:45,960
I'll settle this with you later.

272
00:09:46,559 --> 00:09:47,200
Oh, by the way,

273
00:09:47,799 --> 00:09:48,480
last night when we came,

274
00:09:48,559 --> 00:09:49,480
what did we do?

275
00:09:50,759 --> 00:09:51,320
Oh my.

276
00:09:51,759 --> 00:09:53,120
Prince, what a question.

277
00:09:53,759 --> 00:09:55,399
What else does one do here?

278
00:09:55,399 --> 00:09:56,799
You tell me.

279
00:09:56,840 --> 00:09:58,039
Right, right.

280
00:10:00,919 --> 00:10:01,639
Uh.

281
00:10:01,639 --> 00:10:02,120
Yester-

282
00:10:02,120 --> 00:10:03,919
How many of us came yesterday?

283
00:10:04,399 --> 00:10:05,840
Did you see my Deer of Myriad Treasures?

284
00:10:06,480 --> 00:10:06,720
A deer?

285
00:10:07,720 --> 00:10:08,480
I certainly didn't see one.

286
00:10:09,639 --> 00:10:11,320
But as for you,

287
00:10:11,320 --> 00:10:12,759
there were four of you.

288
00:10:13,360 --> 00:10:14,200
You, Prince,

289
00:10:14,919 --> 00:10:16,840
and this young fellow beside you,

290
00:10:18,240 --> 00:10:19,320
a young lady,

291
00:10:19,600 --> 00:10:20,799
and a foreigner.

292
00:10:20,799 --> 00:10:21,720
That's right,

293
00:10:21,799 --> 00:10:22,600
four of you.

294
00:10:23,399 --> 00:10:24,600
So you're saying

295
00:10:25,120 --> 00:10:27,159
when the princess was with us,

296
00:10:27,559 --> 00:10:28,159
the deer was already gone.

297
00:10:30,200 --> 00:10:31,559
Where did the princess go after?

298
00:10:32,960 --> 00:10:35,200
Halfway through the drinks,

299
00:10:35,360 --> 00:10:36,360
this young fellow here,

300
