take off your clothes,

599
00:20:55,200 --> 00:20:57,519
and show everyone the tattoo on your body.

600
00:20:58,759 --> 00:21:01,359
Last night, after you agreed, you said

601
00:21:01,400 --> 00:21:03,920
you'd tattoo your words onto your body.

602
00:21:04,279 --> 00:21:04,759
Hey!

603
00:21:05,680 --> 00:21:06,720
I already checked his body.

604
00:21:07,039 --> 00:21:07,920
There's nothing there.

605
00:21:07,960 --> 00:21:08,759
Impossible!

606
00:21:09,119 --> 00:21:09,960
Fine, I'll strip!

607
00:21:10,359 --> 00:21:11,119
Tch.

608
00:21:15,720 --> 00:21:16,559
See?

609
00:21:17,119 --> 00:21:17,960
Hey!

610
00:21:19,400 --> 00:21:20,200
There!

611
00:21:20,240 --> 00:21:21,000
Huh?

612
00:21:21,000 --> 00:21:21,799
Ha!

613
00:21:22,720 --> 00:21:23,480
That's not right.

614
00:21:23,480 --> 00:21:24,000
Tch.

615
00:21:24,400 --> 00:21:25,200
Hmph!

616
00:21:25,960 --> 00:21:27,119
Criminal Ouyang Yan,

617
00:21:27,240 --> 00:21:28,559
what do you have to say for yourself?

618
00:21:30,119 --> 00:21:30,559
Ah!

619
00:21:30,559 --> 00:21:31,880
Look at his...

620
00:21:32,880 --> 00:21:34,359
the soles of his feet!

621
00:21:34,640 --> 00:21:35,440
Ha!

622
00:21:36,359 --> 00:21:36,759
Heh.

623
00:21:37,200 --> 00:21:39,039
Come on, come on!

624
00:21:41,759 --> 00:21:42,559
Sigh.

625
00:21:58,720 --> 00:22:00,559
The Prince ordered Ouyang Yan to kill the deer

626
00:22:00,640 --> 00:22:02,200
Ouyang Yan did not want to kill the deer

627
00:22:02,559 --> 00:22:04,440
But the Prince insisted on killing it

628
00:22:04,640 --> 00:22:06,119
Hence, it is hereby proven

629
00:22:06,559 --> 00:22:09,559
The Prince willingly lost the deer to Ouyang Yan

630
00:22:09,640 --> 00:22:12,559
He promised a full-deer banquet for all officials

631
00:22:13,039 --> 00:22:14,119
And will never go back on his word

632
00:22:15,640 --> 00:22:16,640
Oh my goodness

633
00:22:17,559 --> 00:22:19,400
The Deer Prince's foot must be at least size fifty

634
00:22:22,359 --> 00:22:23,200
The verdict is now announced

635
00:22:24,839 --> 00:22:25,799
The Deer Prince is exiled

636
00:22:26,240 --> 00:22:26,839
For brutally killing

637
00:22:26,839 --> 00:22:27,720
Bestowed by the late emperor,

638
00:22:27,720 --> 00:22:30,960
Daliang's top endangered protected animal, the Deer of Myriad Treasures,

639
00:22:31,720 --> 00:22:32,319
The Deer of Myriad Treasures

640
00:22:32,960 --> 00:22:33,960
The means were cruel

641
00:22:34,000 --> 00:22:35,279
And utterly outrageous

642
00:22:35,519 --> 00:22:35,799
Now

643
00:22:36,160 --> 00:22:37,920
With witnesses and evidence in hand

644
00:22:38,160 --> 00:22:39,160
The proof is irrefutable

645
00:22:39,440 --> 00:22:40,519
By the laws of Daliang

646
00:22:40,839 --> 00:22:43,400
A prince who breaks the law is judged like any commoner

647
00:22:43,519 --> 00:22:44,160
From this day forth

648
00:22:44,519 --> 00:22:46,720
He is exiled to the frontier

649
00:22:46,720 --> 00:22:47,720
Court is dismissed

650
00:22:47,720 --> 00:22:48,519
Ah

651
00:22:48,519 --> 00:22:49,119
This...

652
00:22:50,200 --> 00:22:53,720
We were so close to wrapping up, how did it turn out like this?

653
00:22:54,119 --> 00:22:56,440
It's because you two drank too much and ruined everything!

654
00:22:56,960 --> 00:22:58,559
How was I to know the Deer Prince's wine was so strong?

655
00:22:58,640 --> 00:22:59,759
I only had two cups

656
00:23:00,119 --> 00:23:01,400
I'm quitting drinking from now on

657
00:23:01,720 --> 00:23:02,839
I can't drink either

658
00:23:02,960 --> 00:23:04,119
Don't ever let me drink again

659
00:23:05,119 --> 00:23:05,920
Heh

660
00:23:06,319 --> 00:23:08,119
This drug really works wonders

661
00:23:09,359 --> 00:23:10,160
Heh

662
00:23:10,440 --> 00:23:12,559
Let's see what you've got to fight me with now

663
00:23:15,599 --> 00:23:16,400
Hey, hey, hey

664
00:23:17,160 --> 00:23:18,440
We had a deal, didn't we?

665
00:23:18,559 --> 00:23:19,960
You help me become Empress

666
00:23:20,000 --> 00:23:21,160
And I'll give Huahua back to you

667
00:23:21,599 --> 00:23:23,119
Now that Huahua is in my hands

668
00:23:23,119 --> 00:23:24,119
What leverage do you have left?

669
00:23:24,279 --> 00:23:24,759
I...

670
00:23:25,759 --> 00:23:26,319
Let me ask you

671
00:23:26,720 --> 00:23:28,519
If you'd really lost Huahua in the bet yesterday

672
00:23:28,519 --> 00:23:29,799
Would you have stewed her today?

673
00:23:29,799 --> 00:23:30,559
Say it, say it

674
00:23:30,559 --> 00:23:31,319
Look into her eyes and say it

675
00:23:31,319 --> 00:23:32,359
Say it right to her eyes

676
00:23:32,640 --> 00:23:33,960
How could I ever do that?

677
00:23:33,960 --> 00:23:34,839
Huahua

678
00:23:35,559 --> 00:23:36,720
Don't listen to his nonsense

679
00:23:36,720 --> 00:23:38,319
How could I possibly lose?

680
00:23:38,519 --> 00:23:40,359
Besides, our Huahua is so adorable

681
00:23:40,559 --> 00:23:42,559
How could I ever stew you?

682
00:23:42,920 --> 00:23:44,559
Be gentle with Huahua
